{{Quote|Biggest differences in them was their smells which was various degrees of horrible&hellip;Smart enough to listen, stupid enough to be convinced.|Vilmarh Grahrk|<ref name="SW40">[[Star Wars (1998) 40|''Star Wars'' (1998) 40]]</ref>}}
The '''Intelligentsia''' were one of the two main divisions of [[Yinchorri/Legends|Yinchorri]] society, the other being the [[Yinchorri warrior caste|warrior caste]]. They were the natural rulers of the Yinchorri, and had a great affinity for technology. They made up the membership of the [[Council of Elders (Yinchorri)|Council of Elders]]. They were somewhat paranoid and belligerent.

Members of the intelligentsia included [[Sothek]], [[Kardek]], and [[Jorek (Yinchorri)|Jorek]].

